data.title: Hank Williams, The Show He Never Gave – SNEEZY WATERS
data.text:
Sneezy Waters as Hank Williams Sr., with Dixie Seatle, Sean McCann, Jackie Washington, Joel Zifkin, and Sean Hewitt.

Music Producer, Bill Garrett. Produced by Henk Van Der Kolk and William T. Marshall, Executive Producer was Helga Stephenson.

Technical Director, Peter W. Lamb. Directed by David Acomba. Written by Maynard Collins.

The movie was nominated for “The Tex Ritter Award” at The Country Music 1983 Awards Show. It played at the Toronto Film Festival, the London Film Festival and at FILMEX in Los Angeles, California.
